# Sameer Singh Chouhan — Portfolio Website

Personal portfolio and resume site for Sameer Singh Chouhan, FP&A Finance Professional.

## 🚀 How to publish on GitHub Pages

1. Create a new repository on GitHub named exactly: `yourusername.github.io`
   - Replace `yourusername` with your actual GitHub username
   - e.g. if your username is `sameer410`, name it `sameer410.github.io`

2. Upload these files to the repository:
   - `index.html`
   - `Sameer_Singh_Resume.pdf`
   - `README.md`

3. Go to **Settings → Pages** in your repository
   - Source: Deploy from a branch
   - Branch: `main` / `root`
   - Click Save

4. Your site will be live at `https://yourusername.github.io` within a few minutes!

## Files
- `index.html` — The complete portfolio site (photos embedded)
- `Sameer_Singh_Resume.pdf` — Resume for the download button
